---
title: 'Blackened' Tilapia with Pineapple Salsa and Black Bean Rice
description: Quick supper gets a zing of fun Cajun flavours with 'blackened' Tilapia! Cooking tender fish at a high heat gives a dark and flavourful crust in no time.
